OpenStreetMap(R) is open data, licensed under the Open Database License (ODbL)
by the OpenStreetMap Foundation (OSMF). Data and tiles are
(c) OpenStreetMap contributors.

https://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright
https://opendatacommons.org/licenses/odbl/

