## USDA NRCS Soil Survey Geographic Database (SSURGO) — U.S. public domain

Soil Survey Staff, Natural Resources Conservation Service, United States
Department of Agriculture. Soil Survey Geographic (SSURGO) Database for
Georgia. Available online at https://sdmdataaccess.nrcs.usda.gov/.
Accessed 2026.

SSURGO data are produced by the U.S. federal government and are not
subject to copyright protection within the United States.

---

## USGS National Water Information System (NWIS) — U.S. public domain

U.S. Geological Survey. National Water Information System: Web Interface.
Available online at https://waterdata.usgs.gov/nwis. Accessed 2026.

USGS data are produced by the U.S. federal government and are not subject
to copyright protection within the United States. Retrieved through the
USGS-published `dataretrieval` Python package (Hodson, T.O., et al.,
U.S. Geological Survey).

